      "raw_text": "REV. GERTRUDE Won PETZOLD\nGertrude Won Petzold. pastor of the\nFirst Unitarian church, who recent\nly came here from London, and is a\ngenuine English suffraget, will be\none of the chieftains to direct the\nmovement.\n\n\nThe purpose Of this speaking\ncampaign is to elect legislature\nfavorable to a suffrage amendment"
